       He shrugs and looks at Blackheart doubtfully.  "He has never faced the 
kind of force we have gathered here.  He is no match for two Tripredacus 
generals and a field commander (I forgot Tyrael's rank... oops).  We have 
nothing to fear."  He shrugs showing an utter lack of concern.
